  "name": "Progress Version 8.0 Development Environment: The Importance Of Experience-Driven Scalability and Flexibility",
  "description": "Aberdeen evaluates Progress Software's Version 8.0 client-server application development environment (CADE), finding it a scalable, flexible, database-independent toolset. The study examines Progress's SMARTOBJECT components, VPE tools, 4GL language, DataServer architecture, and object-oriented capabilities, concluding Progress 8.0 addresses key IS requirements for complex data-intensive applications through experience-driven engineering.",
